#	Multi-Function-Shield

##	Project info

-	Raspberry 3 HAT
-	IO pin expander MCP23017-E_sp
-	5 buttons: L,R,U,D, Enter
-	3 led indicator
-	LCD 4bit data

##	Pinout

-	i2c address = 0x20(all jumpers NC = 000)

| MCP23017 	| Function 	|
|----------	|----------	|
| GPA0     	| NC       	|
| GPA1     	| LCD_RS   	|
| GPA2     	| LCD_RW   	|
| GPA3     	| LCD_E    	|
| GPA4     	| LCD_D4   	|
| GPA5     	| LCD_D5   	|
| GPA6     	| LCD_D6   	|
| GPA7     	| LCD_D7   	|

| MCP23017 	| Function       	|
|----------	|----------------	|
| GPB0     	| button-2-down  	|
| GPB1     	| button-5-enter 	|
| GPB2     	| button-4-right 	|
| GPB3     	| button-1-up    	|
| GPB4     	| button-3-left  	|
| GPB5     	| led-1-green    	|
| GPB6     	| led-2-yellow   	|
| GPB7     	| led-3-red      	|

